rComments: He has good, enjoyable lectures. Shows that he knows a lot in his field. Wished he spoke up at a higher volume during lectures though. Also, the use of Top Hat is unnecessary (we had to pay for attendance). Overall, good prof.

Really enjoyed his lectures, super informative and interesting, you definitely need to attend class since he doesn't post all of his lectures online. Hard marker and his TAs don't give feedback, I'd advise to attend his office hours, he's hard to reach through email. Super nice and helpful when you reach out. Knows what he's talking about!

rComments: Readings are super interesting, course content super interesting. A lot of people I know have been waiting a couple of years to take this course and it doesn't disappoint.
